    <div class="wrap" style="margin:auto;">
        <div style="margin:auto; margin-left:20px; margin-top:80px;">
            <p id="testing">To add a new class, pick your institution and session. </p><br>
            <div style="margin: auto;">
                <select id="inst" default="pick an institution and session">
                    <option value="defualt" selected="selected">
                        Pick an institution
                    </option>
                </select>
                
                <p>Last, fill out your phone number and provider.</p><br>
                
                <input type="text" placeholder="10 Digit phone number" id="you_phone_nbr">
                <select id="carrier" default="pick a carrier">
                    <option value="defualt" selected="selected">
                        Pick A Carrier
                    </option>
                </select>
                
                <img src="/images/ajax-loader.gif" id="ajax-loader" style="display:none">
                <p> and/or email</p>
                <br><input type="text" id="emailInput" name="email" placeholder="youremail@domain.com"><br>
                <p>Contact you through: </p><br>
                <div class="example">
                   <form>
                        <input id="radio1" type="radio" name="radio" value="text" checked="checked"><label for="radio1"><span><span></span></span>Text</label>
                        <input id="radio2" type="radio" name="radio" value="email"><label for="radio2"><span><span></span></span>Email</label>
                        <input id="radio3" type="radio" name="radio" value="both"><label for="radio3"><span><span></span></span>Both</label>
                  </form>
                </div>
                </div>
                <div class="SubmitButton">
                    <button type="button" id="submitData" style="margin-bottom: 12px;">Get Classes!</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <p>When you finished filling out the forms, select the classes with your mouse, and click "Get Class!"</p><br>
        </div>
    </div>
